<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
  <title>Naghma Tea — شاي نغمة</title>
  <link rel="icon" href="assets/images/favicon.png">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="logo">شاي نغمة — Naghma Tea</h1>
      <nav>
        <a href="#teas">Our Teas</a>
        <a href="#ingredients">Ingredients</a>
        <a href="#process">Process</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <img src="assets/images/hero.jpg" alt="Herbal tea hero" class="hero-img">
      <div class="hero-text">
        <h2>100% Moroccan Herbal Tea</h2>
        <p>Authentic blends crafted with natural Moroccan herbs and spices. Tradition and freshness in every cup.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="teas" class="container teas">
      <h2>Our Signature Blends</h2>
      <div class="grid">
        <article class="card">
          <h3>Moroccan Mint</h3>
          <p class="desc">Refreshing and classic, a symbol of Moroccan hospitality.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Spearmint</li>
            <li>Verbena</li>
            <li>Rose petals</li>
          </ul>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h3>Calming Harmony</h3>
          <p class="desc">A relaxing herbal mix for balance and peace.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Chamomile</li>
            <li>Verbena</li>
            <li>Dried lemon peel</li>
          </ul>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <h3>Citrus Breeze</h3>
          <p class="desc">Zesty and warm, with hints of herbs and spice.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Citrosa (Lemon grass)</li>
            <li>Rosemary</li>
            <li>Cinnamon</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="ingredients" class="container ingredients">
      <h2>Natural Ingredients</h2>
      <p>Each blend is created with handpicked Moroccan herbs and botanicals:</p>
      <div class="ingredients-grid">
        <div><strong>Herbs:</strong><br>Mint, Verbena, Chamomile, Rosemary, Sage, Oregano, Thyme</div>
        <div><strong>Spices & Aromatics:</strong><br>Cinnamon, Clove, Anise, Dried lemon peel, Rose petals</div>
        <div><strong>Special touch:</strong><br>Citrosa, Absinthe, Natural resin (gomme)</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="process" class="container how">
      <h2>Our Process</h2>
      <p>We follow a simple, authentic process to ensure freshness and quality:</p>
      <ol>
        <li>Hand-picking the finest herbs</li>
        <li>Natural drying under the Moroccan sun</li>
        <li>Careful blending and packaging</li>
      </ol>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="container">
      <small>© 2025 Naghma Tea — Moroccan Herbal Blends</small>
    </div>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
